      <item>
        <title>How to select and delete several drafts in iOS</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[sylumer]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <ol>
<li>Tap the “Select” option at the bottom of the draft list to reveal selection markers on each draft.</li>
<li>Tap each selection marker for a draft you want to trash.</li>
<li>Tap the “Operations” option at the bottom of the draft list to display a list of batch processing options.</li>
<li>Select “Trash”.</li>
</ol>
